OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tue 7 Apr to Thu 16 Apr
OL,6,FRather changeable conditions are
OL,7,Fexpected through this period, as a
OL,8,Fseries of Atlantic frontal systems
OL,9,Ftrack eastwards across the UK,
OL,10,Faccompanied by some strong winds at
OL,11,Ftimes. These will bring occasional
OL,12,Fspells of rain or showers, heaviest
OL,13,Fand most frequent in the west and
OL,14,Fnorthwest, with longer drier
OL,15,Finterludes likely in the south and
OL,16,Fsheltered eastern areas. Whilst
OL,17,Ftemperatures will be close to average
OL,18,Ffor the period as a whole, there may
OL,19,Fbe opportunities for some short-lived
OL,20,Fwarm spells in the south and east.
OL,21,FConversely, occasional colder
OL,22,Finterludes in the northwest will bring
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,23,Fthe chance of some wintry showers,
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
OL,24,Fespecially to hills, and overnight
OL,25,Ffrost.
FL,164,160,301,260,100,100
