PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F163A1775135469
OL,1,Wj5hw1~{4k7juhw1{$             G3/3
OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Fri 17 Apr to Fri 1 MayFIt
OL,6,Fis probable that more blocked, or at
OL,7,Fleast slowly evolving, weather
OL,8,Fpatterns will become increasingly
OL,9,Fdominant through the middle of the
OL,10,Fmonth. Whilst confidence is low, this
OL,11,Fmay result in more settled and drier
OL,12,Fconditions overall. There may,
OL,13,Fhowever, still be some more unsettled
OL,14,Finterludes at times, especially in the
OL,15,Fsouth and southwest. Later in April,
OL,16,Fthe probability of more changeable and
OL,17,Funsettled weather increases.
OL,18,FTemperatures will probably be around
OL,19,For a little above normal for the
OL,20,Fperiod as a whole.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
